    "title": "Digital Marketing Manager Vacancy at Hopscotch - 2026 Batch",
    "description": "An exciting career opportunity awaits you at Hopscotch. We are on the lookout for a dedicated Digital Marketing Manager to strengthen our Tiruchirappalli-based team.\n\nAbout Hopscotch:\nHopscotch is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Manage product listings, pricing, and promotions on the platform\n• Track key performance indicators including GMV, conversion rate, and ROI\n• Create engaging content for product pages and social media\n• Manage marketplace relationships with Amazon, Flipkart, and Meesho\n• Analyze sales data and customer behavior to drive revenue growth\n• Monitor and improve Net Promoter Score (NPS) and customer satisfaction\n• Execute digital marketing campaigns across Google, Meta, and other channels\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 12-20 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Content Writing\n• Proficiency in Data Analytics\n• Proficiency in MS Excel\n• Proficiency in Affiliate Marketing\n• Proficiency in CRM Software\n• Proficiency in Performance Marketing\n• Proficiency in Email Marketing\n• Proficiency in SEO/SEM\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• International travel opportunities for senior roles\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 35 LPA - 70 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Tiruchirappalli, Tamil Nadu, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Hopscotch!",
